 Design a network to connect accounts and delivery  departments with each depat. Having 2 pcs , using the given network address of 192.168.40.0


Network address 192.168.40.0
We need 2 subnets – because 2 departments.

Net address-192.168.40.0
Default mask - /24 -255.255.255.0

Range of 1st octet
•	1-126—---------------------class A -------- / 8
•	128-191 -------------------class B---------- /16
•	192-223 ------------------class c -----------/24
192 falls in class c ----------------------------------------/24 ===== 255.255.255.0 ================== first 24 bits network , rest – host address ====== 11111111.11111111.11111111.00000000 
If we convert each octet --- 11111111= 255 thus we get 255.255.255.0.

•	Number of subnets = 2^n
(where n = number of bits borrowed)
I need two subnets -----  2 = 2^n
N has to be 1. (1 we have borrowed 1 bit)
Now new subnet mask is - /25 – 255.255.255.128

Original- /24- 256 IPs
New- /25- split into 2 equal subnets 
•	Each subnet gets -
•	128 IPs in total
•	126 Usable hosts

Subnet calculation—
Subnet 1 – 
•	Network ID-192.168.40.0/25
•	Range – 192.168.40.1 – 192.168.40.126
•	Broadcast   - 192.168.40.127
Subnet 2
•	Network ID – 192.168.40.128/25
•	Range – 192.168.40.129 – 192.168.40.254
•	Broadcast – 192.168.40.255
 


